snippet.title: Real Möbius strips you can ride on
snippet.description:
The Mathologer's mission in this video is to go on a car ride on a REAL Möbius strip. Tag along and enjoy ride. 
Message to all Fast Thinkers and YouTubers in a hurry: If the Mathologer's pace is too slow for you, try watching this video at 2x its original speed via the YouTube player menu. Gets you there in half the time and is a lot of fun, too :)

Update 7 August 2019: J. Hoffman just pointed out to me that there is a science museum in Jena, Germany, The Imaginata that features a Moebius strip roller coaster.   https://youtu.be/ONpK1d0lRds

Enjoy!

Burkard Polster and Giuseppe Geracitano
